room_title: Escape room "Time Chasers" by Morgantown Escape Room in Morgantown
room_description: You are part of an elite group of researchers nick-named "Time Chasers". Through your research, you've discovered a way to travel through time, but something has gone wrong! A malfunction has landed you in a worm-hole. You only have an hour to travel through the ages & retrieve the keystones that will allow you to escape the worm-hole & return home.
